<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Confirmar Código - Honey IA</title>
    <style>
        body { background-color: #121212; color: #fff; font-family: sans-serif; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; height: 100vh; margin: 0; }
        .card { background: #1e1e1e; padding: 40px; border-radius: 12px; border: 2px solid #FFB900; width: 100%; max-width: 400px; text-align: center; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 185, 0, 0.2); }
        h2 { color: #FFB900; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        p { color: #ccc; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; }
        input[type="text"] { width: 80%; padding: 12px; margin: 20px 0; border: 1px solid #555; border-radius: 6px; background: #2a2a2a; color: white; text-align: center; font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: 4px; font-weight: bold; }
        button { width: 100%; background: #FFB900; color: #000; border: none; padding: 12px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; cursor: pointer; transition: 0.2s; }
        button:hover { background: #e0a300; }
        .erro { color: #ff4a4a; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 15px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="card">
    <h2>Confirmação de Conta 🐝</h2>
    <p>Enviámos um código de ativação de 6 dígitos para o e-mail: <br><strong><%= email %></strong></p>
    
    <% if (erro) { %>
        <div class="erro"><%= erro %></div>
    <% } %>

    <form action="/confirmar-codigo" method="POST">
        <input type="text" name="codigo" placeholder="000000" maxlength="6" required autocomplete="off">
        <button type="submit">Ativar Conta Gratuita</button>
    </form>
</div>

</body>
</html>
